question.lot_name: Vladimir Guerrero 2002 Louisville Slugger Game Used Bat
question.overview_raw: A 34', 32.5 oz. Louisville Slugger bat produced during the 2002 labeling period and used by Vladimir Guerrero. The H238' model lumber is uncracked and shows ball marks and ball stitch impressions on the right, left and back barrel. Blue, red and black rack streaks are also visible. A light coat of pine tar adorns the handle. Guerrero's number '27' is on the knob in black marker. Moderate game use. LOA from PSA DNA
